==Documentation==
This template creates a full character page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
| Name || Display name of the character
|-
| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
| Aliases || Alternative names (comma-separated)
|-
| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
| RealName || Character's real name (if different)
|-
| Gender || Male/Female
|-
| Birthday || Birth date
|-
| Death || Death date (if applicable)
|-
| Games || Games this character appears in (comma-separated)
|-
| Franchises || Franchises this character belongs to
|-
| Friends || Allied characters (comma-separated)
|-
| Enemies || Enemy characters (comma-separated)
|-
| Concepts || Related concepts (comma-separated)
|-
| Locations || Associated locations (comma-separated)
|-
| Objects || Associated objects (comma-separated)
|-
| People || Real people associated with character (comma-separated)
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
{{Character
| Name = Mario
| Guid = 3005-177
| Deck = Nintendo's iconic plumber...
| RealName = Mario Mario
| Gender = Male
| Birthday = 1981-07-09
| Games = Games/Super_Mario_Bros, Games/Super_Mario_64
| Friends = Characters/Luigi, Characters/Princess_Peach
| Enemies = Characters/Bowser
}}

== Overview ==
Your wiki content here...

{{CharacterEnd}}
